<div id="rightcol">
<h1 class="heading_grey">Pay, Performance and Productivity Consulting</h1>

<div class="floatleft img_left" id="index_img_pay"></div>

<p>Westminster Associates is a New England based full-service human resource and compensation consulting firm specializing in compensation, performance management and productivity improvement for all organizations. We work <b><i>for and with</i></b> our clients in a closely supportive relationship of exceptional service and value. Our goal is to grow your company by improving the contributions of your human resources. We establish reward strategies; job, market and pay equity; incentive plans, including alternative reward strategies, and performance appraisal programs for performance improvement. <a href="aboutwestminster.php">Read Full Story</a></p>


<h2 class="heading_grey clrfloat">Ask A Consultant</h2>

<div class="floatright img_right" id="index_img_consult"></div>

<p>“Ask A Consultant” is a <strong>Free Service</strong> of Westminster Associates for both employers and employees. We will answer your questions on any topic related to compensation, benefits, labor laws, performance, and productivity, etc. Just send your question to us via our website and we will e-mail our answer to you.</p>





